# Gate OUTPUT, regenerated on every run — evidence, not source.
#
# `shoot.mjs` writes e2e/shots/ and `dashboard-scenarios-run.mjs` writes
# e2e/scenario-shots/ (one screenshot per stage of every scenario). They exist
# to be LOOKED at right after a run — several real defects this project fixed
# were visible truths no assert was watching — but they are reproducible from
# source and would otherwise churn hundreds of binaries per commit.
#
# NOTE: e2e/goldens/ is deliberately NOT ignored. Those are the blessed
# reference frames; they are the point of the visual gate.
e2e/shots/
e2e/scenario-shots/
